00:37:09.980 --> 00:37:10.530
Venga.

00:37:13.780 --> 00:37:15.530
Señora, ¿qué te pasa?

00:37:16.130 --> 00:37:16.820
Nada.

00:37:17.170 --> 00:37:18.500
Sigamos con lo nuestro.

00:37:19.170 --> 00:37:19.780
Vamos.

00:37:32.900 --> 00:37:33.530
Abuela,

00:37:34.650 --> 00:37:36.570
